## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

The Guardtime Blockchain-enabled Service Broker has the following requirements:

* A Guardtime KSI blockchain service endpoint, port, administrator account, and administrator password. See the [License](#license) section below for information about obtaining a Guardtime KSI 60-day free trial.  
* The Redis for PCF tile. The Guardtime Blockchain-enabled Service Broker uses a Redis datastore to hold metadata and binding information. For more information about how to install Redis for PCF, see the [documentation](https://docs.pivotal.io/redis/index.html). 

<p class="note"><strong>Note</strong>: In a development environment, you can run a local Redis server instead of the Redis for PCF tile. See the <a href="http://redis.io/topics/quickstart">Redis documentation</a> for more information.</p>

